to represent him,

07:04.924 --> 07:09.345
and it just shit in its own hand
and mushed it in the face of the jury,

07:10.221 --> 07:12.014
it would have gotten the same sentence

07:12.098 --> 07:14.142
-Ted got making an effort.
-[laughing]

07:14.684 --> 07:16.686
[applause and cheering]

07:18.438 --> 07:22.567
And collectively can we agree?
Stop harping on his appearance.

07:22.650 --> 07:24.527
He was an average-looking guy,

07:24.610 --> 07:27.738
but they can't stop talking about,
"Oh, my God, he was charming.

07:27.822 --> 07:29.532
Ted Bundy was so handsome."

07:29.615 --> 07:30.450
No, he wasn't!

07:30.533 --> 07:33.744
-He was handsome in that pool of people.
-[audience laughs]

07:36.122 --> 07:36.956
Okay?

07:37.039 --> 07:41.002
In the group of men who have murdered
and raped 40 or more women...

07:41.169 --> 07:42.879
[continued laughter]

07:43.254 --> 07:44.505
Ted's a catch.

07:44.589 --> 07:46.591
[laughing and applause]

07:48.384 --> 07:49.552
Ted's a nine.

07:51.345 --> 07:53.806
But how about some kind,
understanding words

07:53.931 --> 07:55.016
for the rest of us, huh?

07:55.099 --> 07:57.143
How about a little leeway
for other average men?

07:57.226 --> 07:58.769
I realize I'm only a five,

07:58.853 --> 08:01.355
