people lose their fucking minds.

08:39.936 --> 08:41.145
-Oh, my God.
-[cheering]

08:41.229 --> 08:42.813
[applause and whooing]

08:43.064 --> 08:45.107
"Comedy has gone too far.

08:46.067 --> 08:48.069
Comedians have got to stop.

08:48.152 --> 08:51.072
