cancel these comedians.

08:51.155 --> 08:53.533
Hold on, I'd like to hear Ted's take.",

08:53.699 --> 08:55.701
[audience laughs]

08:57.453 --> 08:58.871
It's fucking psychotic.

08:58.955 --> 09:01.040
I'm not saying the documentaries
shouldn't exist,

09:01.123 --> 09:04.085
